Name: Spaghetti Carbonara
Ingredients: Spaghetti, eggs, pancetta, parmesan cheese, black pepper, salt
Directions: Cook spaghetti. Fry pancetta. Mix eggs and cheese. Combine all with pepper.

Name: Chicken Alfredo
Ingredients: Chicken breast, fettuccine, heavy cream, butter, garlic, parmesan
Directions: Cook pasta. Sauté chicken and garlic. Add cream and cheese. Mix with pasta.

Name: Vegetable Stir Fry
Ingredients: Broccoli, bell peppers, carrots, soy sauce, garlic, ginger, oil
Directions: Chop vegetables. Stir-fry with garlic and ginger. Add soy sauce. Serve hot.

Name: Beef Tacos
Ingredients: Ground beef, taco shells, lettuce, tomato, cheese, taco seasoning
Directions: Cook beef with seasoning. Fill shells with beef and toppings.

Name: Pancakes
Ingredients: Flour, milk, eggs, baking powder, sugar, butter
Directions: Mix batter. Pour onto griddle. Flip when bubbles form. Serve with syrup.

Name: Caesar Salad
Ingredients: Romaine lettuce, croutons, parmesan, Caesar dressing
Directions: Toss lettuce with dressing. Add croutons and parmesan.

Name: Tomato Soup
Ingredients: Tomatoes, onion, garlic, basil, broth, cream
Directions: Sauté onion and garlic. Add tomatoes and broth. Blend and simmer.

Name: Grilled Cheese Sandwich
Ingredients: Bread, cheese, butter
Directions: Butter bread. Add cheese between slices. Grill until golden.

Name: Chocolate Chip Cookies
Ingredients: Flour, sugar, butter, eggs, chocolate chips, baking soda, salt
Directions: Mix ingredients. Drop spoonfuls on tray. Bake until golden.

Name: Beef Stew
Ingredients: Beef chunks, potatoes, carrots, onions, beef broth, herbs
Directions: Brown beef. Add vegetables and broth. Simmer until tender.

Name: Omelette
Ingredients: Eggs, milk, cheese, salt, pepper
Directions: Beat eggs. Pour into pan. Add cheese. Fold and cook until set.

Name: Greek Salad
Ingredients: Tomatoes, cucumber, olives, feta cheese, olive oil, oregano
Directions: Chop vegetables. Mix with olives, feta, and dressing.

Name: Lasagna
Ingredients: Lasagna noodles, ricotta, ground beef, tomato sauce, mozzarella
Directions: Layer noodles with sauce and cheese. Bake until bubbly.

Name: Garlic Bread
Ingredients: Baguette, butter, garlic, parsley
Directions: Spread garlic butter on bread. Bake until golden.

Name: Fried Rice
Ingredients: Rice, eggs, peas, carrots, soy sauce, oil
Directions: Scramble eggs. Add rice and veggies. Stir-fry with soy sauce.

Name: Banana Bread
Ingredients: Bananas, flour, sugar, eggs, butter, baking soda
Directions: Mix all ingredients. Pour into loaf pan. Bake until done.

Name: Tuna Salad
Ingredients: Canned tuna, mayonnaise, celery, onion, salt, pepper
Directions: Mix all ingredients. Serve chilled.

Name: Mashed Potatoes
Ingredients: Potatoes, butter, milk, salt, pepper
Directions: Boil potatoes. Mash with butter and milk. Season to taste.

Name: Shrimp Scampi
Ingredients: Shrimp, garlic, butter, lemon juice, parsley, pasta
Directions: Sauté garlic and shrimp in butter. Add lemon juice. Serve with pasta.

Name: French Toast
Ingredients: Bread, eggs, milk, cinnamon, sugar, butter
Directions: Dip bread in egg mixture. Cook on griddle until golden.
